Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.82,0:56:02.48,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\blur10}I'm looking out the window.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:02.48,0:56:17.64,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\blur10\t(1627,2586,\3c&H000000H)}forgetting the weight resting on my shoulders, on my shoulders.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:18.18,0:56:28.85,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}We all grew up not so long ago, it seems.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:29.42,0:56:50.04,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}I go outside and see the season is changing slowly.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:50.04,0:56:57.32,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}Time passes by unevenly from one second to the next.
Dialogue: 1,0:56:57.32,0:57:02.85,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}We once were so young and innocent.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:02.85,0:57:08.99,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}I remember…
Dialogue: 1,0:57:23.99,0:57:38.15,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}Nothing can replace the bond forged from our camaraderie.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:38.15,0:57:43.81,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}closer than anything else…
Dialogue: 1,0:57:43.81,0:57:54.01,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}I watched us all gorw up over time, and I know that days may pass.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:54.01,0:57:57.93,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}things may change, you might go away.
Dialogue: 1,0:57:57.93,0:58:06.10,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}but I am so certain you're looking out for me from now on.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:06.10,0:58:14.07,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}and I will keep nurturing the friendship that we had made long ago.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:14.07,0:58:18.05,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}I'm keeping you sage, keeping you sound.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:18.05,0:58:28.80,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}Nothing can ever compare to the tenderness that is given through brotherhood.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:28.80,0:58:41.44,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}I wait for the furture to come, and hope that I'll meet you.
Dialogue: 1,0:58:43.80,0:58:56.53,ED EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fax-0.1}I'm holding on to hope, though I'm sure I won't be all on my own.
